Purpose:			Deletes a Sorting Method Object by calling a Utility

Parameters:			_realSortingMethod	CM_SortingMethod	The real sorting method to use in the utility
					_passport			CM_Passport			The passport to use to hold errors and perform other tasks

Return Value:		NONE

Date			Who		Reason
07 June 2023	navpw1	Initial creation TFS: 57813 (58438)

*/

